{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"上善若水","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQDZRnEAypu396mq2FzNVSFDcMGHy6ibvCRwJqzEKS41S4DRTTa1MtbrRicbrl2TH0YkyiaKLVAL2dD6/0","content":"贫穷导致教育资源的缺失，受教育程度越低，越难改善贫穷的面貌","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8332,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492655020000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"月时纪","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZnlcvTEdxwCaoOlSYRWabE3plmsicuRXNtKcnKNK4T7AdiabtBnz7rMkAscAqWtHPpLrA3f6FY1pRg/0","content":"1.因为贫穷，所以能获取的资源有限，包括师资物资，导致教育水平低下；<div>2.教育水平低下，导致人们能从事的工作有限，能挣到的钱也有限；</div><div>3.互为因果，贫穷与教育水平也是一种恶性循环。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":8139,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492613593000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"迷迭香","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-14","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6bWV5FUyboCIOk2icGvegOZ7qmwDXVPlm0pmyu0tuemmkIaDqE1O6xCdX1tVMLNtwTvuVYVOMKQG3A/0","content":"可能的关联形式:1.因为太贫穷，父母没钱供孩子上学，导致教育缺乏；2.因为贫穷，没有人原来到这样的贫困地区做教师从事教育行业，所以教育缺乏；3.因为教育缺乏，人们受教育不足导致文化水平低下，没能力致富，生活更贫穷；4.在极度贫困地区，对教育不重视，当地政府更注重解决温饱问题，人民的受教育意识也不强，同时出现了贫穷和教育缺乏两种现象；5.贫困地区家庭为了增加劳动力，多生孩子，家庭负担沉重同时导致了贫穷和教育缺乏。总之，贫穷和教育缺乏二者可能相互影响，互为因果，也可能第三方因素同时导致这两种现象相关联。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7692,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1492137363000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-07","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">因为缺乏教育，所以缺少知识和技能，从而无法获得相对高收入的工作机会，导致贫穷。同时，由于贫穷，可能温饱都是问题，所以无力承担教育支出，或者周围人都是贫穷的，没有教育改变命运的意识，忽视教育的作用，导致教育的缺乏。</span><br></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7346,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491541349000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"盛夏tl","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-06","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQLZSOLpBibDcibZ6sFXGjaugXibNJwMAvZF35uJNo0TzNd8uGdLrfymhDiav0qNFFCZzEIQIxyrWNEPw/0","content":"因为缺乏教育就无法获得更多的输出型人才所以导致该地区整体经济模型畸形造成该地区越来越贫乏","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7263,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491434372000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"潇洒鳕鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98UyLlHC2Q1gMdxzMwDhQicAb4RP8PgibVuS6OEZoCGk0aIWo8mMahY8wu6ic8YFFqdsInJgJAaxbe58CIgsSXQC94U/0","content":"<p>贫穷与教育的缺乏之间存在着复杂的联系：</p><p>1、由于家庭的贫穷，导致适龄学童无法接受应有的教育；由于政府的贫穷，导致无法提供应有的教育；这些最终都会导致教育的缺乏。</p><p>2、由于缺乏教育，没有获得应有的知识和技能，导致无法赚取足够的钱，因此经济上贫穷；<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">由于缺乏教育，没有获得应有的文化与修养，导致思想上的贫穷。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px;\">3、贫穷和教育的缺乏也可能并非是以上直接互为因果的关系，也可能只是相关的因素关系。</span></p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6370,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491404666000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jenny","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoIfMsKLER8Nypic0GAEMQNhWH5ILCc3l1sO0iaB8nCIc9BLEdxIThXGnNtM55ozuBic03EicuCPictyib2/0","content":"贫困和教育缺乏的关系很复杂：既可以是因为家庭贫困没有钱让孩子接受教育，又可以是因为长期的教育缺乏使得贫困加剧。两个因素相互影响，互为因果的恶性循环。同时存在可能性是，由于传统观念的闭塞影响或者政府的腐败不作为，导致了贫困和教育缺乏。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7240,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491386127000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小小云","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-05","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/hglMZuicA3iauTIlciaKXMtjOkia7eibkITySvUExH5dicgdSdEHl6Y1FLwVWDq7XOjt0EbfuA0EIVRVGCgKLzyU1mIhTtk3AYMl8R/0","content":"弄清二者关联得先分开研究二者，贫穷可以从生活水平，健康水平，环境水平，最重要的是人口数量。教育从当地经济水平和教育投入的量考虑。<div>越贫穷的地方，生活没有基本保障，教育越缺乏，通过教育和技术改进生活，实现财富，改变机遇就越少。</div><div>教育投入的越少，人口数量越多，地区越贫穷。</div><div>贫穷和教育还受当地资源匮乏，经济滞后的影响。</div><div>二者相互影响，穷导致接受教育人少，接受教育的人少，改变贫穷的机遇和力量越小。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7224,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491362876000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Huiling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaSibLgdZoEbwz0j0N3JqxibHIXiaPrzMn0EqK1SiaZOmddjg9AV56OBReweicArAW1qtlxy36IJF04ibrj2/0","content":"互为因果","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7193,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491307835000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"kerry","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-04","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay5cUlGv2ibxydlESCOjsMG6yNquicDV2grtRHY4e6BREibMTu7aYqiaYHGMSVmVfneOdxIhRkLicP5at1/0","content":"让我想到美国作家对于贫困的体验，我的理解如下<img src=\"http://static.iqycamp.com/application-20170404160022-81reabcb5-.jpg\" style=\"max-width:90%\"><br>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7179,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491292843000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"敏","submitUpdateTime":"2017-04-01","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay36u84xJJa5xZVbSorVQsjiaRtdKff23d2pibDW0oSbVW3r0CUiaQtIg47Itf131L8acNXmLucqib4ibt/0","content":"<p>1.因为贫困，所以食物摄取不足，得不到足够的营养，无法正常上课。</p><p>2.因为贫困，人们注意力只放在继续生存上。教育属于更高层次的追求。</p><p>3.因为贫困，没有能力吸引好的老师或进行必要的教育投入，无法开展教育。</p><p>4.因为缺乏教育，劳动者的技能无法得到提高，生产效率无法提高。</p><p>5.因为缺乏教育，人们的知识水平无法得到提高，无法应用新事物，不明白贫穷的原因。</p>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6981,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1491030408000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"咕咕","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoAOwic4GNKoz5oR3ECE0v0lAicujK9wBbRPMVWrjBNRath8ZicUnKVKP1TicLlXAlKrf2HJNO0Vv5SH5/0","content":"1.贫困导致了教育资源的匮乏<div>2.教育获取不足让当地的人们走不出贫困</div><div>3.贫困地区往往在地理环境不好的地方，而这些地方又很难引入教育资源，也很难普及，接受教育机会太少，就会导致更加贫困。</div><div>4.贫困地区生活艰苦，少有师资愿意去，当地教育质量得不到提高，获得教育机会的学生也倾向于走出去不回来，因此发达地区优秀人才不断涌入，教育资源也随之愈加丰富。</div>","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5434,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490974915000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"锦慕兰","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-29","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XpSLeBeWNiaS3skBBT8HsSPCyTJe0kT5cTVYOdIHeuEGdvfS3eHvDbZuYZcRIMxiaz0lVQjiadx2BdTtgw0bzCCn0/0","content":"1.由于所在地区贫穷，导致没有更多的资源投入在教育上。\n2.正是因为缺乏教育，该地区人民思想落后，生产力低下导致无法脱贫。\n3.由于地理位置的劣势，自然资源匮乏或交通不发达；又或者该地区传统生活方式和文化的保守和固化，人员流动性不高，都可能导致生活贫穷和教育缺乏。\n4.贫穷和教育缺乏互为因果，恶性循环。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6518,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490771683000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"张梦路","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-24","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6ZaLoY2RXU5FZibDrTsS1osmryDqKeuAvlF9licJ4nKDicnJ1HjwXTbvxdlVJj5oBJgqhR72iaGMxLcib1jJGsyWnUnj/0","content":"仓禀实而知礼节，衣食足而知荣辱。 反之也成立。\n\n教育的缺失使人们缺少赚钱的技能和机会，因此贫穷。\n\n贫穷恶化了教育的环境和水平。由于生活水平及认知的局限，教育得不到重视，教育资源不足。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5303,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490362001000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"El.","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELtgmmibEickAfib5gqpJia8eU8BgdbpVtiagqxQibOos1ow0iaSsnbntHv6muZESK2MAeTp7VJzfsibNx8ibw/0","content":"因为贫困无大量资金投入教育资源。反过来因为缺乏教育，无法摆贫困思维冲破枷锁，继续维持贫困现状。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5225,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490256896000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-23","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8hWCY4rsU5ic7YX8NSbKTQ1jqib9icr5cJBexUUicYhHibyRcicc1Y9Hxmc5hFqdxgaUNjiaBH4HIahUdE/0","content":"1.因为贫穷导致更关注温饱，对教育不重视\n2.因为贫穷无法大规模发展教育事业\n3.因为缺乏教育，发现经济的能力有限，无法摆脱贫穷\n4.贫穷和教育的缺乏相互促进，互为因果","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":5133,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490233101000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":true},"code":200}
